dct_description_sm: Title taken from top margin of map. In lower left marginof sheet one: "10465.1 August 1946". Shows boundaries of the Allied occupation sectors of Berlin superimposed on base map "Verkehrsplan Berlin" l Includes inset: SonderkarteInnestad 1:20,000. Showing the boundaries between the administrative zones.
